metadata.title: SAVITA 54PCS St. Patrick's Day Window Stickers Shamrocks Ornament Set Shamrock Window Cling Stickers for Home Office Decoration Party Supplies Gifts (4 Sheets)
features: Package Content: You will receive 4 sheet 54pcs shamrock window cling stickers. The variety is nice and each sheet is different. The largest shamrocks is about 9.5 inch high.
Material: St. Patrick's Day Window Stickers are made with PVC material. It sticks based on static electricity instead of glue. Shamrock window stickers is shiny and easy to store and carry.

Double-Sided Design: The double sided clings are absolutely amazing on the windows. Each shamrock is uniquely designed to add St. Patrick's Day festival atmosphere. Vibrant color is seen both indoors & outdoors.
Easy to Use: Shamrock window clings are simple to put up and adhere great. They are easy to remove or readjust if necessary, no residue when removed either.

Wide Application: Shamrocks ornament set are great window decorations for St. Patrick's Day. They can be applied to mirrors, windows, tiles, refrigerators. Non-adhesive static clings are not suitable for car windows, as the heat may cause them to fall off.
